:: StoryTitle
Strange Town


:: StoryData
{
  "ifid": "D4B2A1C3-9E7F-4A02-B8D6-5C3E1F2A0B94",
  "format": "Harlowe",
  "format-version": "3.3.9",
  "start": "Start"
}


:: Start
Once upon a time, there was a traveller who arrived in a strange new town.

Feeling weary, they spotted a café and stepped inside.

What is your character's name?

(set $name to "")
(live: 0s)[
  (if: $name is "")[You'll need a name to continue.]
]

(input-box: bind $name, "=X=")

[[Continue->Choose-drink]]


:: Choose-drink
Once upon a time, there was a traveller named //''$name''// who arrived in a strange new town. Feeling weary, they spotted a café and stepped inside, desperate for something to drink.

It was a cold morning. What did they crave?

[[A hot drink->Hot-drink]]
[[A cold drink->Cold-drink]]


:: Hot-drink
(set: $drink to "a hot drink")

The café only had two hot options. Which did they choose?

[[Tea->Companion]]
[[Coffee->Companion]]


:: Cold-drink
(set: $drink to "a cold drink")

The café had two cold options. Which did they choose?

[[Soda->Companion]]
[[Iced tea->Companion]]


:: Companion
Once upon a time, there was a traveller named //''$name''// who arrived in a strange new town. Feeling weary, they spotted a café and stepped inside, desperate for (print: $drink). They sat down — and then, uninvited, someone appeared.

Who sat down at their table?

[[A mysterious stranger->The-secret]]
[[A talking cat->The-secret]]


:: The-secret
(set: $companion to "")

(if: $companion is "")[
  The stranger leaned in close.

  What secret did they whisper?

  (input-box: bind $companion, "=X=")

  [[Continue->Reaction]]
]


:: Reaction
Once upon a time, there was a traveller named //''$name''// who arrived in a strange new town. They ordered (print: $drink) and sat down. Just then, a visitor appeared from nowhere and whispered: //"(print: $companion)."//

How did $name react?

[[Laughed it off->Ending-laugh]]
[[Packed their bags immediately->Ending-flee]]
[[Decided to investigate->Ending-investigate]]


:: Ending-laugh
Once upon a time, there was a traveller named //''$name''// who arrived in a strange new town. They ordered (print: $drink) and sat down. A mysterious visitor appeared and whispered: //"(print: $companion)."// ''$name simply laughed it off and ordered another round.''

//The end.//

[[Start again->Start]]


:: Ending-flee
Once upon a time, there was a traveller named //''$name''// who arrived in a strange new town. They ordered (print: $drink) and sat down. A mysterious visitor appeared and whispered: //"(print: $companion)."// ''$name immediately packed their bags and left town before sunset.''

//The end.//

[[Start again->Start]]


:: Ending-investigate
Once upon a time, there was a traveller named //''$name''// who arrived in a strange new town. They ordered (print: $drink) and sat down. A mysterious visitor appeared and whispered: //"(print: $companion)."// ''$name decided to investigate — and was never quite the same again.''

//The end.//

[[Start again->Start]]
